Class Request.Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.lucichkevin.cip.kalima.Request.Status
  • Enclosing class:
    Request

    public static class Request.Status
extends java.lang.Object
    Indicates the current status of the request. Each status will be set only once during the lifetime of the request.
